# T3 Stack Project Overview

This is a **T3 Stack** project named "edu-one" using modern full-stack TypeScript technologies.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 15 with App Router
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Database**: Drizzle ORM (configured, not yet implemented)
- **API**: tRPC for type-safe APIs
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS (basic setup)
- **State Management**: TanStack Query (React Query)
- **Code Quality**: Biome for linting/formatting
- **Package Manager**: pnpm

## Current Project Structure
- `src/app/` - Next.js App Router pages and layouts
  - `_components/` - Private components for app directory
  - `api/trpc/` - tRPC API route handler
  - `layout.tsx` - Root layout component
  - `page.tsx` - Homepage
- `src/server/` - Backend API routes and database logic
  - `api/` - tRPC router definitions
  - `db/` - Database configuration and schemas
- `src/trpc/` - tRPC client configuration
- `src/styles/` - Global styles and CSS

